'''黑喉歌鸲'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Calliope obscura''}}）为[[鶲科|鶲科]][[野鸲属|野鸲属]]的[[鸟类|鸟类]]。分布于泰国以及[[中国大陆|中国大陆]]的[[甘肃|甘肃]]、[[陕西|陕西]]等地，常见于针叶林的竹丛或灌丛间。该物种的模式产地在[[甘肃|甘肃]]。<ref name='id3032'/>

黑喉歌鸲非常罕见，1886年在中国甘肃被发现后，总共只观察到58只成年黑喉歌鸲<ref>{{cite news|author=Matt Walker|title=Rare blackthroated blue robins spotted in China|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/nature/26851727|accessdate=2014-04-15|newspaper=BBC|date=8 April 2014|archive-date=2014-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140415091821/http://www.bbc.co.uk/nature/26851727|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|coauthors=Alström, Per; Zhang, Yongwen; Gao, Xuebin; Gong, Huisheng; Holt, Paul I.; Quan, Qing; Yin, Zuohua; Lei, Fumin|title=Rediscovery of an enigmatic Chinese passerine, the Blackthroat Calliope obscura: plumage, vocalizations, distribution, habitat choice, nesting and conservation|journal=Journal of Ornithology|date=2013-10-23|volume=155|issue=2|pages=347–356|doi=10.1007/s10336-013-1009-5|last=Song|first=Gang}}</ref>。

